Products.SmallFormatDescription: Birds Eye Peas Garden Field Fresh
Products.FullDescription: Birds Eye Peas Garden Field Fresh
Products.RichDescription:
We grow the best quality, vegetables right here in Australia and take great pride in being able to support our local farming Communities.

Our Farmers don't just grow vegetables, they care for them, and some have been doing so for over 50 years.

From the Rich Soils of Tasmania to the sunny highlands of NSW and Queensland, our farms are located in the best growing regions Australia has to offer. Our Vegetables are always picked at their peak, then Snap Frozen from fresh to lock in all of nature's goodness.

 - All Natural Ingredients

- High in Fibre (When Cooked)

- Source of Vitamin C (When Cooked)

- Source of Folate (When Cooked)

 
 
Please note: Due to local vegetable shortages, we have had to temporarily change our source of frozen vegetables from local to international across several Birds Eye SKUs. During the transition period, you may find imported frozen vegetable stock on shelf. Please review the product packaging for specific detsils, including country of origin information, when you receive this product. This is a temporary changeover with the intent to fill a supply gap and improve the availability for our customers. We're working hard to bring you Australian vegetables from the best local farmers as soon as we can.
